content:
I firmly believe that for the NFT space to achieve the success we all want, it must capture the hearts and minds of everyday people 

To truly go mainstream, NFTs need to be part of a culture where a new generation grows up with these digital IPs

Same way as older generations grew up with icons like Pokémon and Hello Kitty

I believe Teddies is well positioned to make this happen, right from day one 

Our art is universally appealing, transcending age, gender, race and ethnicity

The teddy bear is a character that resonates with everyone

A character that can easily be part of various domains like fashion, gaming, entertainment and media

With Teddies my goal is to not just launch an NFT collection but a cultural phenomenon 

A phenomenon that has the potential to become as ingrained in our lives as the most beloved and timeless IPs
